-- Yemen Blames Al-Qaeda for Ambush on Patrol That Killed Five Soldiers
-- Nasser Morshid
-- 2010-07-22T11:59:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-22/yemen-blames-al-qaeda-for-ambush-that-killed-five-soldiers-in-east.html

          
          
             Five Yemeni soldiers were killed and
a sixth injured in an attack on their patrol vehicle in the city
of Ataq, in the country’s eastern province of Shabwa.  
 Al-Qaeda gunmen carried out the attack in coordination with
separatists, the director of security in Shabwa, Ahmed Al-
Makdashi, said today in a statement.  
